            "<p>How do I install Steam?</p>",
            '<ol>  \t<li>Ensure that you are logged in as an administrator on the machine which you would like to install Steam on</li>  \t<li>If you have previously installed Steam and are reinstalling to remedy a problem with your prior installation, please see the <a href="kb_article.php?ref=9609-OBMP-2526" title="Uninstalling Steam">Uninstalling Steam</a> topic for instructions to remove any prior Steam installations</li>  \t<li>Check the <a href="kb_article.php?ref=1456-EUDN-2493" title="Troubleshooting Network Connectivity">Troubleshooting Network Connectivity</a> topic to ensure the required ports for Steam are open on your network</li>  \t<li>Download and run the Steam Installer from <a href="http://www.steampowered.com/v/index.php?area=getsteamnow&amp;" title="Get Steam Now">www.steampowered.com</a></li>  </ol>    <p>If you encounter any difficulty with your installation, please see the <a href="kb_article.php?ref=1223-QROC-4460" title="Contacting Steam Billing and Support">Contacting Steam Billing and Support</a> topic for instructions to contact Steam Support.</p>',
