            "Duplicate CD Key",
            "<p>I receive a &quot;Duplicate CD Key&quot; error when I try to register my CD Key - what should I do?</p>  ",
            '<p>&nbsp;</p>    <p>If you purchased a <b>new</b> retail game and are receiving <i>Duplicate CD Key</i> error, please contact the retailer where the game was purchased to obtain a new copy of the game.</p>    <p>If the retailer is unable or unwilling to assist you, it is recommended that you contact <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_cat.php?id=19">the game&#39;s support</a> for further assistance.</p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <div class="important">  <h3>Important:</h3>    <p>A retail CD Key may only be registered to <span class="bold">one</span> Steam Account. CD Keys are associated with your Steam Account, not the computer on which the game is installed.</p>    <p>Please see the <a href="kb_article.php?ref=4988-DHXV-7272" title="Guide: Resetting a Lost Password">Resetting a Lost Password</a> article for instructions to retrieve your lost Steam account if it is possible that you have registered your CD Key in the past.</p>  </div>    <p>&nbsp;</p>  ',
