            "Contacting Ubisoft Support",
            "<p>How do I contact Ubisoft Support?</p>  ",
            '<div class="section">  <p>To create a support ticket with Ubisoft Support, please follow the steps below:</p>    <ol>  \t<li>Go to <a href="http://support.ubisoft.com/" title="Ubisfot Support">http://support.ubisoft.com/</a></li>  \t<li>Click <b>Uplay Sign In</b> toward the top right of the page and enter your Uplay Account credentials. If you have not yet created an account, click <b>CREATE A UPLAY ACCOUNT</b> to create the account.</li>  \t<li>Select the <b>Options</b> button at the top right of the screen. In the drop-down menu, select <b>Go To: Contact Support</b>.</li>  \t<li>You will now see the Open a Support Case page. Select <b>Email Us</b> for a support ticket or <b>Start Chat</b> for a live chat within the listed hours of operation.</li>  \t<li>Use the drop-down menus to select the Platform, Product, and Category.</li>  \t<li>In the SUBJECT field, type a brief description of your issue.</li>  \t<li>In the HOW CAN WE HELP YOU? field, explain your issue with as much detail as possible.</li>  \t<li>Optionally, select <b>+ Add Files</b> to attach relevant files to your case, such is images or MSInfo files.</li>  \t<li>You will then be presented a list of possible resolutions for the issue (SUGGESTED FAQS). If this resolves your issue, you may close the window. If this does not resolve your issue, click on the <b>Submit My Case</b> button to submit the ticket or the <b>Submit &amp; Start Chat</b> button to begin your live chat.</li>  \t<li>The next page will confirm your ticket submission and present you with some additional information along with your 8-digit Reference Number. Ubisoft Support will then respond to your ticket as soon as possible via the requested method.</li>  </ol>  </div>  ',
