            '<div class="important">  <h3>Important:</h3>    <p>This will&nbsp;only add a shortcut to your game in the Steam client. This will not allow you to download updates for your game through Steam, nor allow you to use this game as proof of ownership for your Steam account.</p>  </div>    <h4>Adding a shortcut to a non-Steam game</h4>    <ol>  \t<li>Launch Steam.</li>  \t<li>Click the <span class="bold">Games</span> menu, choose <span class="bold">Add&nbsp;a Non-Steam Game to My Library.</span></li>  \t<li>Browse for games on your computer or put a check next to the&nbsp;game(s) you wish to add to the&nbsp;<strong>Library.</strong></li>  \t<li>Click on <span class="bold">"Add Selected Programs"</span>.</li>  </ol>    <p>&nbsp;</p>  ',
