            "<p>Where can I find support information for the Playstation 3 version of The Orange Box?</p>",
            '<h4>EA Support</h4> <p>Please visit the EA Games website for support: <a href="http://support.ea.com/cgi-bin/ea.cfg/php/enduser/std_alp.php?p_cv=&amp;p_pv=2.4006&amp;p_prods=2308%2C4006&amp;p_cats=0&amp;p_hidden_prods=&amp;p_sid=MJHb*MTi&amp;p_lva=&amp;p_li=&amp;p_accessibility=0&amp;p_redirect=&amp;p_page=1&amp;prod_lvl1=2308&amp;prod_lvl2=4006&amp;cat_lvl1=0&amp;p_search_text=&amp;p_new_sea ">EA Support</a>.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <h4>Game Issue: Can not connect to multiplayer servers in Team Fortress 2</h4> <p>A Playstation Network account is required to play Team Fortress 2 Online. For more information about the Playstation Network, please visit Sony\'s website: <a href="http://www.us.playstation.com/PS3/Network" title="The Playstation Network">http://www.us.playstation.com/PS3/Network</a></p> <p>Please make sure that the following ports are open in your router\'s configuration settings:</p> <ul>     <li><span class="bold">TCP Ports</span>: 13505, 18450, 18455</li>     <li><span class="bold">UDP Ports</span>: 18455, 2000-5000</li> </ul> <p>If you are not sure how to open ports on your router, please consult your router\'s instruction manual for more information.</p> <p>More information about EA Online can be found on the official EA Games website: <a href="http://www.ea.com/" title="EA Games">http://www.ea.com/</a></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>',
