            '<div class="important">  <h3>Important:</h3>    <p>If you have <span class="bold">not</span> recently purchased a game please see the <a href="kb_article.php?ref=5168-EUIA-6643" title="No games listed in the My Games Tab">Games are Missing from the Library</a> article for instructions.</p>  </div>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <h3>Recent Purchases</h3>    <p>Steam may allow you to play the game while it is in the process of authorizing your credit card.</p>    <p>In the event that your credit card purchase is declined, Steam will remove the games from&nbsp;the Library&nbsp;list. The next time you try to play the game, Steam will ask if you want to attempt the purchase again.</p>    <p>You must make a valid purchase in order to play if your payment was declined for any reason.</p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>  ',
