            '<p>All Valve Store orders are currently processed by ForFansByFans. For more information or support with a Valve Store order, please contact ForFansByFans directly via one of the methods listed on this page: <a href="https://www.forfansbyfans.com/contactus">https://www.forfansbyfans.com/contactus</a>.</p>    <p>Please also include the following information with your message:</p>    <ul>  \t<li>Your Valve Store Sales Order number</li>  \t<li>The email address you used when you placed the order</li>  \t<li>A brief description of your issue</li>  </ul>    <p>Questions about games purchased on Steam should be sent to <a href="kb_article.php?ref=1223-QROC-4460">Steam Billing and Support</a>.</p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>',
