            "",
            '<h5>Finding DLC in the store</h5>    <p>If a game offers additional downloadable content, you can find it on the store from the base game page or by searching for it.</p>    <p><img src="http://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/support/faq/dlc_instore.jpg" width="600px;" /></p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <h5>Finding DLC I own in my library</h5>    <p>DLC owned by your account can be viewed in your library. From the Library tab in the Steam Client, select a game and the DLC section will show if you own DLC and if it\'s been installed.</p>    <p><img src="http://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/support/faq/dlc_inlibrary.jpg" width="600px;" /></p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>  ',
