            '<p>Often, disk permissions become inconsistent over time. Some of these problems have a negative impact on Steam. If Steam does not start, or games do not launch, please try this first:</p>    <ul>      <li>Click on <span class="bold">Applications &gt; Utilities &gt; Disk Utility</span></li>      <li>Click on the <span class="bold">First Aid</span> tab</li>      <li>Let the repair process finish and then restart Steam to see if this corrects the problem</li>  </ul>    For older versions of OSX:  <ul>      <li>Click on <span class="bold">Applications &gt; Utilities &gt; Disk Utility</span></li>      <li>Select your <span class="bold">System Disk</span></li>      <li>Click on the <span class="bold">First Aid</span> tab</li>      <li>Click on <span class="bold">Repair Disk Permissions</span></li>      <li>Let the repair process finish and then restart Steam to see if this corrects the problem</li>  </ul>',
