            '<ol>      <li>Open the <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/about/">Steam client</a> and go to Settings:</li>      <img src="images/faq/PasswordReset/settings.png" alt="Steam Settings" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px" />      <li>Click <i>Change Password or Secret Question...</i>:</li>      <img src="images/faq/PasswordReset/changepw.png" alt="Change Password" style="border:1px solid grey;max-width:95%;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px" />      <li>Select <i>I want to change my password</i> and choose <i>Next:</i></li>      <img src="images/faq/PasswordReset/step1.PNG" alt="Step 1" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px" />      <li>Enter your current password (If you do not know it, please <a href="kb_article.php?ref=1223-QROC-4460">Contact Support</a>):</li>      <img src="images/faq/PasswordReset/currentpw.png" alt="Current Password" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px" /> \t<br />      <li>      <ol> \t\t\t<br />          <li>An email from Steam Support will be sent to the email address associated with your Steam account. Please check your spam/trash folder if you do not see the email within 24 hours or <a href="kb_article.php?ref=1223-QROC-4460">Contact Support</a>.</li>          <li>Enter the 5 character code from the email into the first field.</li>          <li>Type your new password into the second field. It must not be a previous password and must meet the password strength  requirements.</li>          <li>Choose <i>Next</i> to change your password.</li>          <img src="images/faq/PasswordReset/code.png" alt="Step 1" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px" /> \t\t</ol>          </li>          <li>Your password has been changed and you will receive a confirmation email in your inbox.</li>          <img src="images/faq/PasswordReset/success.PNG" alt="Finish" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px" /> </ol>'