            "",
            '<p><a name="client"></a></p>  <h3>Using the Steam client:</h3>  <ol>      <li>Create a new Steam account by downloading and installing the Steam application (please follow the link below to download the application):<br />      <p><a href="http://store.steampowered.com/about/">http://store.steampowered.com/about/</a></p>      </li>      <li>Click the &quot;Create a New Account...&quot; button from the Steam login page and follow the prompts      <p>&nbsp;</p>      </li>  </ol>  <p><a name="website"></a></p>  <h3>Using the Steam website:</h3>  <ol>      <li>Go to the following website: <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/login/">https://store.steampowered.com/login/</a></li>      <li>Click on Join Steam</li>      <li>Fill out the form and click on Create My Account</li>  </ol>  <p>&nbsp;</p>',
