            "Adding a PPA Repository for the Latest Intel Drivers",
            "<p>If your machine is running an Intel graphics card, we recommend running the latest graphics drivers. These drivers, developed and approved by Intel, are distributed using the x-updates PPA (personal package archive). By default, this PPA is not added to the Ubuntu 12.04 repository list. The following procedure adds this repository.</p>",
