            '<link href="https://cdn.steamstatic.com/apps/dota2/css/deskpro_kb_no_col.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />  <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b><img alt="" border="1" height="188" src="http://cdn.dota2.com/apps/dota2/images/international2015/compendium/stretch_goals/cursor_pack.jpg?v=valveisgoodatcaching" width="590" /></b></span></span></p>    <ul>  \t<li><b><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="#requirements">CURSOR TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS </a></span></span></b></li>  \t<li><b><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="#design">DESIGN CONSIDERATIONS </a></span></span></b></li>  \t<li><b><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="#submission">INSTRUCTIONS FOR SUBMISSION </a></span></span></b></li>  \t<li><b><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="#examples">EXAMPLE CURSOR PACKS</a></span></span></b></li>  </ul>  ',
            '<h2><a name="requirements"></a></h2>    <h2><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b>CURSOR TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS</b></span></span></h2>    <ul>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Each cursor must be 32 pixels by 32 pixels, 24-bit RGB color with 8-bit alpha channel.</span></span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;">The format of the resulting image must be bmp (with transparency).</span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">It is no longer necessary to provide .ani files for cursors.</span></span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">The hotspots locations for the cursors will be the same as those set for our default cursors.</span></span></li>  </ul>    <p><a name="design"></a></p>    <h2><font face="Arial" size="3"><b>DESIGN CONSIDERATIONS</b></font></h2>    <ul>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;">The hues, greyscale values, and line widths of the cursors need to read well in all map locations and lighting situations.</span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;">The edges of the images should be as clean as possible. </span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;">Don&#39;t force a lot of details into the cursor images if it makes them too busy or hard to read. Keep the design simple and stylized to display as clearly as possible.</span></li>  </ul>    <p><a name="submission"></a></p>    <h2><b style="font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">INSTRUCTIONS FOR SUBMISSION</span></span></b></h2>    <ul>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Refer to the <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=2858-RTHJ-5696">Submitting Items</a> page for important general information about testing and submitting items.</span></span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Cursor Packs are submitted under the <strong>&quot;Images...&quot;</strong> category.</span></span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">The preview loadout will show an icon with the default cursors but you will see your cursors when you continue through to the game.</span></span></li>  \t<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">When done testing in game, return to the Workshop Tool and follow the steps to publish your&nbsp;Cursor Pack to the Workshop.</span></span></li>  </ul>    <p><a name="examples"></a></p>    <h2><b style="font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">EXAMPLE CURSOR PACK</span></span></b></h2>    <p><font face="Arial" size="3"><span style="line-height: 25.6px;">Download the <a href="http://media.steampowered.com/apps/dota2/images/workshop/guidelines/cursors/example_valve_cursor_pack.zip">Valve Example Cursor Pack</a></span></font></p>    <p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.dota2.com/workshop/">Dota 2 Item Workshop&nbsp;Guidelines Homepage</a></span></span></p>  ',
