            '<p><a href="#ie">Internet Explorer</a></p>  <p><a href="#firefox">Firefox</a></p>  <p><a href="#safari">Safari</a></p>  <p><a href="#chrome">Chrome</a></p>',
            '<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><a name="ie"></a>Internet Explorer</h3>  <h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">Verified through version 10</h4>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <ol style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Click&nbsp;<strong>Tools&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;<strong>Internet Options</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Select the&nbsp;<strong>General&nbsp;</strong>tab.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Under &quot;Browsing History,&quot; uncheck the checkbox for&nbsp;<strong>Delete browsing history on exit</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Click&nbsp;<strong>OK&nbsp;</strong>to close the &quot;Internet Options&quot; window.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Close and restart your browser.</li>  </ol>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><a name="firefox"></a>Firefox</h3>  <h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">Verified through version 22</h4>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <ol style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Choose the menu option for your computer:<br />      <ul type="disc" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">PC: Select&nbsp;<strong>Tools&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;<strong>Options</strong>.</li>          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Mac: Select&nbsp;<strong>Firefox&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;<strong>Preferences</strong>.</li>      </ul>      </li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Select the&nbsp;<strong>Privacy</strong>&nbsp;tab.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Under &quot;History&quot;:<br />      <ul type="disc" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">If it is set to &quot;Use custom settings for history,&quot; uncheck the checkbox for&nbsp;<strong>Clear history when Firefox closes</strong>.</li>      </ul>      </li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Click<strong>&nbsp;OK</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Close and restart your browser.</li>  </ol>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><a name="safari"></a>Safari</h3>  <h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">Verified through version 5.1.7</h4>  <p style="margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Currently, Safari does not support clearing your history when you exit. Here\'s how to check Safari for extensions that might be automatically clearing cookies:</p>  <ol style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Choose the menu option for your computer:<br />      <ul type="disc" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Mac: Click<strong>&nbsp;Safari&nbsp;</strong>(          <p style="margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px;"><img alt="Safari Gear Icon" align="absMiddle" width="34" height="22" src="http://help.yahoo.com/library/YAHOO/IMAGES/General/gen_sfricg_01.png" style="border: 0px; max-width: 100%;" /></p>          gear icon in newer versions) |&nbsp;<strong>Preferences</strong>.</li>          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">PC: Click&nbsp;<strong>Edit&nbsp;</strong>or&nbsp;<strong>Tools&nbsp;</strong>(          <p style="margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px;"><img alt="Safari Gear Icon" align="absMiddle" width="34" height="22" src="http://help.yahoo.com/library/YAHOO/IMAGES/General/gen_sfricg_01.png" style="border: 0px; max-width: 100%;" /></p>          gear icon in newer versions) |&nbsp;<strong>Preferences</strong>.</li>      </ul>      </li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Select the&nbsp;<strong>Extensions&nbsp;</strong>tab.<br />      <ul type="disc" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">All installed extensions will display. Click an extension to see details about what it does.</li>          <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">If you need help with an extension, please contact the developer of that extension.</li>      </ul>      </li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Close the &quot;Preferences&quot; window.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">If you made any changes to extensions, close and restart your browser.</li>  </ol>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><a name="chrome"></a>Chrome</h3>  <h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">Verified through version 28</h4>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <ol style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Click the&nbsp;<strong>Tools icon&nbsp;</strong><img width="17" height="15" src="http://help.yahoo.com/library/YAHOO/IMAGES/General/gen_chrmopt_all_01.png" alt="Three horizontal bars" style="border: 0px; max-width: 100%;" />&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>Settings</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Click&nbsp;<strong>Show advanced settings</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">In &quot;Privacy,&quot; click<strong>&nbsp;Content settings</strong>.&nbsp;</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Under &quot;Cookies,&quot; verify that the checkbox is unchecked for&nbsp;<strong>Keep local data only until I quit my browser</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">When you\'re done, click&nbsp;<strong>Done</strong>.</li>      <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px;">Close and restart your browser.</li>  </ol>',
