            '<ul>  \t<li><a href="#price_match">I recently purchased a gift that is now on sale. Can I refund the difference?</a></li>  \t<li><a href="#giftmyself">I purchased a game as a gift, can I add it to my own account?</a></li>  \t<li><a href="#redeemed_gift">My friend has already redeemed my gift, can I still get a refund?</a></li>    </ul>',
            '<style type="text/css">.hidden {  \t\tdisplay: none;  \t}    \t.hidden .instruction-list {  \t\tmargin-bottom: 0;  \t}    \t.instruction-list img {  \t\tmargin-bottom: 45px;  \t}  </style>  <h1 id="price_match">I recently purchased a gift that is now on sale. Can I refund the difference?</h1>    <p>We are unable to refund the difference in price; however, you <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=6695-QIKM-7966">may request a refund</a> for the initial gift and repurchase it at the current sale price.</p>    <p>Unredeemed gifts may be cancelled and returned to your inventory.</p>      <p>To cancel a pending gift:</p>    <ol class="instruction-list">  \t<li>Log in to your Steam client and click &quot;Games&quot; in the upper left-hand corner</li>  \t<li>From the menu, click &quot;Manage Gifts &amp; Guest Passes&quot;</li>  \t<li>Select the gift within your Steam Inventory and click &quot;Send gift...&quot; as seen below:</li>  \t<li>Select the &quot;Return the gift to your account&quot; option and click &quot;Next&quot;</li>  </ol>      <p>Please note, approved refunds may take up to 7 days to appear in your account. For payment methods that do not qualify for direct deposit, refunds will only be available as Wallet credit.</p>        <h1 id="giftmyself">I purchased a game as a gift, can I add it to my own account?</h1>    <p>To redeem a gift to your own account:</p>    <ol class="instruction-list">  \t<li>Log in to your Steam client and click &quot;Games&quot; in the upper left-hand corner</li>  \t<li>From the menu, click &quot;Manage Gifts &amp; Guest Passes&quot;</li>  \t<li>Within your Steam Inventory, select the gift and click &quot;Add to my library&hellip;&quot; as seen below:</li>  </ol>    <p><img alt="Gift inventory" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/steam_gift_inventory.jpg" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>      <h1 id="redeemed_gift">My friend has already redeemed my gift, can I still get a refund?</h1>    <p>A refund may be issued for any gift that was purchased within fourteen days and has been played less than two hours by the gift recipient.</p>    <div class="important">Note: To request a refund on a Steam Gift, we will need the gift recipient to first initiate the refund and approve the removal of this purchase from their account.</div>    <ul>  \t<li>Have the gift recipient initiate the process by requesting a refund as outlined below.</li>  \t<li>Once the refund has been verified by the gift recipient, please go to <a href="http://help.steampowered.com">help.steampowered.com</a> and create your <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=6695-QIKM-7966">refund request</a>.</li>  </ul>    <ol class="instruction-list">  \t<li>The gift recipient should go to <a href="http://help.steampowered.com">help.steampowered.com</a> and log in with their Steam Account.</li>  \t<li>Once logged in, click on &quot;Games, Software, etc.&quot;</li>  \t<p><img alt="Giftee Refund 1" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/refunds/giftee-refund1.png" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>  \t<li>Find and click on the gift in the provided list</li>  \t<p><img alt="Giftee Refund 2" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/refunds/giftee-refund2.png" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>  \t<li>Click the problem that is occurring with the product</li>  \t<p><img alt="Giftee Refund 3" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/refunds/giftee-refund3.png" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>  \t<li>Next, click &quot;I\'d like to request a refund&quot;</li>  \t<p><img alt="Giftee Refund 4" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/refunds/giftee-refund4.png" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>  \t<li>Finish the request by clicking the box to remove the gift from your account and allow the original purchaser to request a refund</li>  \t<p><img alt="Giftee Refund 5" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/refunds/giftee-refund5.png" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>  \t<li>If the gift recipient has not initiated the gift refund process, you will see the following when attempting to request a refund</li>  \t<p><img alt="Giftee Refund 6" src="https://support.steampowered.com/images/faq/gifting/refunds/giftee-refund6.png" style="margin-bottom:15px;" /></p>  </ol>  </div>                ',
