            "Item and Trading Bugs",
            '<p>We encourage users to work with other members of the community in order to resolve common issues with items. Please use the game\'s discussion hubs as well as developer forums to discuss possible bugs within the game. These forums are regularly read by users encountering similar issues, as well as developers that may be able to address them.</p>  <ul style="list-style: none; margin: 35px auto 0; width: 100%;">      <li style="display: inline-block; width: 32.5%; text-align: center; padding: 0; font-size: 18px;"><a href="http://dev.dota2.com/">Dota 2</a></li>      <li style="display: inline-block; width: 32.5%; text-align: center; padding: 0; font-size: 18px;"><a href="http://steamcommunity.com/app/440/discussions/">Team Fortress 2</a></li>      <li style="display: inline-block; width: 32.5%; text-align: center; padding: 0; font-size: 18px;"><a href="http://steamcommunity.com/app/730/discussions/">CS:GO</a></li>  </ul>',
