            "How do I change my Steam account password?",
            '<div class="important">  <h3>Try to self-recover your account or contact Steam Support:</h3>    <p style="padding-top: 10px;">You can use <a href="https://help.steampowered.com/wizard/HelpWithLogin">the Help site to try to self recover your account</a> or contact Steam Support if you are unable to.</p>    <p style="padding-top: 10px;">If you are unable to complete the self recovery process, Steam Support will verify the account is yours and recover it for you.</p>  &nbsp;    <p>When contacting Steam Support try to provide as much of the following as possible:</p>  &nbsp;    <ol class="question-list">  \t<li><a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=2347-QDFN-4366#proof">Proof of account ownership</a></li>  \t<li>Any possible Steam Account login names</li>  \t<li>Any possible email addresses used on the account</li>  </ol>  </div>  ',
            '<p>Open the <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/about/">Steam client</a> and go to Settings (Preferences on a Mac):<img alt="Steam Settings" src="images/faq/PasswordReset/settings.png" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:15px;margin-top:5px" /></p>    <p>Select &quot;Change Password...&quot;: <img alt="Change Password" src="images/faq/PasswordReset/pwreset1.png" style="border:1px solid grey;max-width:95%;margin-bottom:15px;margin-top:5px" /></p>    <p>Enter your current password:<br />  <img alt="Current Password" src="images/faq/PasswordReset/currentpw.png" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-top:5px" /></p>    <p>(Don&#39;t remember your password? You can <a href="https://help.steampowered.com">use the Help site to reset it</a>)</p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <p>An email from Steam Support will be sent to the email address associated with your Steam account. If you don&#39;t receive an email, make sure to check your spam folder.</p>    <p>Enter the 5 character code from the email and enter a new password. <b>NOTE:</b> It must not be a previous password and must meet the password strength requirements.</p>    <p><img alt="Step 1" src="images/faq/PasswordReset/code.png" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:15px;margin-top:5px" /></p>    <p>When you&#39;ve completed changing your password, you&#39;ll receive confirmation by email. <img alt="Finish" src="images/faq/PasswordReset/success.PNG" style="border:1px solid grey;margin-bottom:15px;margin-top:5px" /></p>  ',
