            "How to Report a Scammer, Hijacker or Phisher",
            '<p>Reporting a scammer, hijacker or phisher through their Steam Profile will always be better than submitting a Steam Support ticket containing your report. A community report includes the best information about the interaction between your accounts, and is quicker to review and act on.</p>    <p>To avoid scams in the future, ensure that you know the methods that a malicious user may use to attempt to scam. You can find detailed information&nbsp;in our&nbsp;<a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=3415-WAFH-6433">Scam FAQ</a>.</p>',
            '<p class="MsoNormal">If you are scammed, phished or hijacked, please use the Report feature built into Steam:</p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <ul>  \t<li>Go to the Steam profile of the offending user</li>  \t<li><o:p></o:p>Click the \'More\' drop-down button located at the top right of the page</li>  \t<li><o:p></o:p>Choose &quot;Report Profile&quot; <o:p></o:p></li>  </ul>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <p><img alt="" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/support/faq/report_malicious_4.jpg" title="Report Profile Screenshot" width="100%" /></p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <ul>  \t<li><o:p></o:p>Select the offense which best describes the behavior you are reporting.<o:p></o:p></li>  </ul>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <p><img alt="" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/support/faq/report_malicious_1.jpg" title="Report Profile Screenshot" width="100%" /></p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <ul>  \t<li><o:p></o:p>Further specify the activity you observed.<o:p></o:p></li>  </ul>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <p><img alt="" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/support/faq/report_malicious_2.jpg" title="Report Profile Screenshot" width="100%" /></p>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <ul>  \t<li><o:p></o:p>Select the violation, write a short statement about your interaction with this user, and hit &quot;Submit Report&quot; <o:p></o:p></li>  \t<li><o:p></o:p>You can also choose to block this user.<o:p></o:p></li>  </ul>    <p>&nbsp;</p>    <p><img alt="" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/support/faq/report_malicious_3.jpg" title="Report Profile Screenshot" /></p>    <hr />  <p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>    <p class="MsoNormal">If you have been scammed, we recommend that you review our <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=3415-WAFH-6433">Scam FAQ</a>, the <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=8912-WEYU-8454">Recommended Trading Practices</a> article and our <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=9958-MJDG-3003">Steam Item Restoration Policy</a> for more information.</p>    <p>For information on how to safeguard an account, please read our <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=1266-OAFV-8478">Account Security Recommendations</a><span class="SteamChinaExclude"> and our <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/actions/ReportSuspiciousLogin">Account Phishing</a> articles</span>.</p>    <p>If you have lost items due to your account being compromised, please see our <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=9958-MJDG-3003">Steam Item Restoration Policy</a> article</a> for more information.</p>    <p><o:p></o:p></p>',
