            "<p>To opt into beta depots:</p>  <ol>  \t<li>Open the Steam client and navigate to your <b>Library</b>.</li>  <li>From the CS:GO page, open the <b>Properties</b> window from the <b>Manage menu</b>  <li>Select the <b>Betas</b> tab  <li>Select the beta you would like to opt into  <li>Launch CS:GO to play the game with its Beta changes.</li>  </ol>  <p>To opt out of the beta and resume playing the current version of the game, select 'None' in the drop down on the betas tab. This will require you to re-download the current public files.</p>",
