            '<!DOCTYPE html>  <html>  <head>  \t<title>Index Shipping</title>  </head>    <body>    <div class="container">  \t<img src="https://support.steampowered.com/steamvr/FitGuide/GuideHeader.png" style="width:100%;height:260px;">  \t<div class="bottom-left"><h1 class="page-title">VALVE Index System Requirements</h1></div>  \t<div class="bottom-right"><a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_cat.php?id=106" style="color: white">&lt; Back to Support</a></div>  </div>    <div class="black-section">  \t<h4>Minimum</h4>  \t\t<ul>  \t\t\t<li>OS: Windows 10, SteamOS, Linux</li>  \t\t\t<li>Processor: Dual Core with Hyper-Threading</li>\t  \t\t\t<li>Memory: 8 GB RAM</li>\t  \t\t\t<li>Graphics: Nvidia GeForce GTX 970 / AMD RX480</li>\t  \t\t\t<li>Network: Broadband Internet connection</li>\t  \t\t\t<li>Additional Notes: Available DisplayPort (Version1.2) and USB (2.0+) Port required  </li>\t  \t\t</ul>    \t<h4>Recommended</h4>  \t\t<ul>  \t\t\t<li>Processor: Quad Core+</li>  \t\t\t<li>Graphics: Nvidia GeForce GTX 1070 or better</li>\t  \t\t\t<li>Additional Notes: Available USB (3.0+) Port required for Headset Pass-Through Camera</li>\t  \t\t</ul>\t    \t<h4>Tracking</h4>  \t\t<p>The Index Headset requires a minimum of 1 (2 recommended) Base Stations for tracking. Index is compatible with both the original Vive Base Stations and the 2.0 versions available on the <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1059570/Valve_Index_Base_Station/">Steam Store.</a></p>    \t<h4>Controllers</h4>  \t\t<p>The Index Headset is compatible with Vive and Vive Pro Wands in addition to <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1059550/Valve_Index_Controllers/">Valve\'s Index Controllers.</a></p>    \t<h4>Available Ports</h4>  \t\t<p>The Index Headset requires that your system has the following ports available:</p>  \t\t<ul>  \t\t\t<li>1 x DisplayPort 1.2+ for headset display</li>  \t\t\t<li>1 x USB 3.0+ for headset cameras</li>  \t\t</ul>  </div>    <div class="content-section">  \t<h4>Laptop Users</h4>  \t\t<p>Laptops that use integrated graphics rather than a dedicated GPU that meets or exceeds our system requirements may not work with Index.</p>  \t\t<p>Please note: Index does not support HDMI, and will not work with DisplayPort to HDMI adapters.</p>  </div>    </body>    <style class="Index-reservations-css" type="text/css">    \t.right_col {  \t\tdisplay: none;  \t}    \t.left_col {  \t\twidth: 100%;  \t}  \t  \t#content {  \t\tfont-family: "Motiva Sans Light", "Motiva Sans", Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;  \t\t-moz-box-sizing: border-box;  \t\tbox-sizing: border-box;  \t}    \t#content .pagetext {  \t\tpadding: 13px 13px 0;  \t\tbackground: none;  \t}    \t#content #question .content-section {  \t\tbackground: #202020;  \t\t  \t}  \t\t  \t#content #question .black-section {  \t\tbackground: #000000;  \t\tpadding: 13px 13px 0;  \t}    \t#question {  \t\tborder-top: none;  \t\tmargin-bottom: 0px;  \t\tnone repeat scroll 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);  \t}    \t#question > h1:first-child {  \t\tdisplay: none;  \t}  \t  \t#wrapper {  \t\t  background: black;\t  \t}  \t  \t.content-section {          position: relative;  \t\tpadding: 13px;  \t\tbackground: none repeat scroll 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);  \t\tmargin-bottom: 0px;  \t\tz-index: 999;  \t}  \t  \t.black-section {  \t\tposition: relative;  \t\tpadding: 13px;  \t\tbackground: none repeat scroll 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);  \t\tmargin-bottom: 0px;  \t\tz-index: 999;  \t}    \t.content-section img {  \t\tdisplay: block;  \t\tmargin: 20px auto 0;  \t}  \t  \th1 {  \t\tfont-size: 2.5em;   \t}  \t  \th4 {  \t\tColor: #DA70D6;  \t}  \t  \tsup {  \t    vertical-align: top;  \t    font-size: smaller;  \t}  \t  \t.topic-description-container {  \t\tfont-size: 16px;  \t}  \t  \t.topic-header-text {  \t\tmargin-bottom: 10px;  \t}    \t.nav-container-float{  \t\twidth: 50%;  \t\tfloat: left;  \t\tcolor: #67c1f5;  \t\tfont-weight: bold;  \t}    \t.clear-float {  \t\tclear: both;  \t\theight: 0;  \t\tcontent: hidden;  \t}    \thtml {  \t\tmin-height: 100%;  \t    margin: 0;  \t}  \t  \tbody {  \t\tmin-height: 100%;  \t    margin: 0;  \t\tbackground-color: black;  \t}  \t  \t.horiz-rule {  \t\theight: 1px;  \t\twidth: 100%;  \t\tborder-top: 1px solid #fff;  \t\tmargin: 25px 0;  \t}  \t\t  \t.column {  \t  float: left;  \t}    \t.left {  \t  width: 20%;  \t  margin: 0 auto;  \t  padding: 30px  \t}    \t.right {  \t  width: 80%;  \t}  \t  \t.half {  \t  width: 40%;  \t}  \t  \t.row:after {  \t  content: "";  \t  display: table;  \t  clear: both;  \t}\t\t  \t  \t.container {  \t\tposition: relative;  \t\tcolor: white;  \t}    \t.bottom-left {  \t  position: absolute;  \t  bottom: 8px;  \t  left: 16px;  \t  vertical-align: top;  \t}    \t.bottom-right {  \t  position: absolute;  \t  bottom: 8px;  \t  right: 16px;  \t  z-index: 999;  \t}    </style>  </html>',
